      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ 425°F/ Gas 7</p><p>Cut the<strong> potatoes </strong>(skins on) into chips</p><p>Add the <strong>chips </strong>to a baking tray with a generous drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 25-30 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
